{"tid":217884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(支那高鐵)  狗食既飯盒，搵笨七既服務員","createTime":"2017-04-26T06:26:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-26T08:44:44.000Z","uid":29314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5a0f86233c37c1a59b09480b5077a6c6e4ef0f20","tid":217884,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T06:26:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170426/photo/bkncn-20170426060127366-0426_05011_001_03b.jpg?20170426062238\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170426%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170426060127366-0426_05011_001_03b.jpg%3F20170426062238&h=490f90fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地媒體調查發現，售價45元（人民幣．下同）的飯盒，成本最高15元，而15元的飯盒成本僅7元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170426/photo/bkncn-20170426060127366-0426_05011_001_02b.jpg?20170426062238\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170426%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170426060127366-0426_05011_001_02b.jpg%3F20170426062238&h=c82af5db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於飯盒銷量與餐飲服務員的業績、福利掛鈎，15元的飯盒利潤空間太小，故餐飲服務員售賣時，...不會主動推銷15元飯盒.....，詢問後才說有，<span style=\"color: red;\">餐飲服務員多推銷高價飯盒。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170426/photo/bkncn-20170426060127366-0426_05011_001_04b.jpg?20170426062238\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170426%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170426060127366-0426_05011_001_04b.jpg%3F20170426062238&h=7817a78b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n............<br />\n<br />\n「他們當然不會主動推薦15元的，太便宜了，利潤空間小。」一名業內人士透露，列車上的餐飲服務員除了基本工資外，就是績效工資，還有佣金，與銷售業績掛鈎。另有業內人士計算高鐵飯盒的成本，發現售價45元的飯盒，成本最高15元，而15元的飯盒成本僅7元。<br />\n<br />\n..............陝西省物價局一名客服人員坦言，火車上飯盒的價格屬於市場放開調節價，由鐵路部門自主定價，不受物價部門監管。"},{"pid":"32ef7591362eac603b614abacdaed5457e441d21","tid":217884,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T06:33:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a556203671435355b2f974d5572ab8d83b67cde6","tid":217884,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T06:34:37.000Z","msg":"講真真係接受到佢咁做<br />\n至少平民開口問佢唔會收埋<br />\n就算日本小鎮車站閘前店都係咁"},{"pid":"8b8804adec4b6c4f4a2fa44f555064cb1c705341","tid":217884,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T06:34:43.000Z","msg":"有無得FIGHT?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s27.postimg.org/io51nd1pf/PIE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs27.postimg.org%2Fio51nd1pf%2FPIE.jpg&h=9e27fa28&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d7126db290b58297f1d6c843a4251726b42c3c57","tid":217884,"uid":2583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T06:38:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無得FIGHT?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s27.postimg.org/io51nd1pf/PIE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs27.postimg.org%2Fio51nd1pf%2FPIE.jpg&h=9e27fa28&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n因航<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64327796d184922f4f6b774ad7fdbbe6d73ea36d","tid":217884,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T06:42:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無得FIGHT?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s27.postimg.org/io51nd1pf/PIE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs27.postimg.org%2Fio51nd1pf%2FPIE.jpg&h=9e27fa28&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n因航<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n果盤咩黎？"},{"pid":"feb1df6d6dd583eff67210a7519ec3ae9adfe8ed","tid":217884,"uid":498,"like":0,"dislike":0